Korçak, Sabit, M. Kemal Öztürk, Süleyman Çörekçi, Barış Akaoğlu, Hongbo Yu, Mehmet Çakmak, Semran Sağlam, Süleyman Özçelik, and Ekmel Özbay. “Structural and Optical Properties of an InxGa1−xN/GaN Nanostructure.” Surface Science 601, no. 18 (September 2007): 3892–3897.
