====[http://apl.aip.org/resource/1/applab/v91/i6/p061923_s1 Plasma ehnancement of metalorganic chemical vapor deposition and properties of Er2O3 nanostructured thin films<ref name="M. M. Giangregorio">M. M. Giangregorio et al., “Plasma ehnancement of metalorganic chemical vapor deposition and properties of Er2O3 nanostructured thin films,” Applied Physics Letters, vol. 91, no. 6, pp. 061923-061923-3, Aug. 2007</ref>]====

