====[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0022024805006056 Temperature induced shape change of highly aligned ZnO nanocolumns<ref name="J. Y. Park">J. Y. Park, I. O. Jung, J. H. Moon, B.-T. Lee, and S. S. Kim, “Temperature induced shape change of highly aligned ZnO nanocolumns,” Journal of Crystal Growth, vol. 282, no. 3-4, pp. 353-358, Sep. 2005</ref>]====

